originalText.text: The last review is himself. Don't use him. He made all sorts of promises about doing prep by puttying and sanding, doing careful work on woodworking, and putting down protection on floors and mirrors, and did very little or none. Got paint everywhere. Tried to wipe it and put paint in my sink/drain. He sprayed detailed woodwork when he said he would brush it. Applied putty badly with fingers, when he did at all, then painted over it immediately before drying. Didn't sand anything. Finished by putting primer on over top coat while pretending to do touchups. Screamed at me when I pointed any of this out, and then called me a ballbuster and left me with a poor job and a big mess.
